a5d1664d292c"],

Cell["\<\
In the forthcoming analysis, it will be useful to have a list with the name \
of features (genes). For the purposes of this practical, you can refer to the \
genes as \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]gene 1\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]gene 2\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote],... \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]gene 7\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7799009898518705`*^9, 
  3.7799010398812246`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"abc7b0b9-216b-4454-9c86-\
60cc8762bb37"],

