Cell[TextData[{
 "Due to the repeated genotypes, to define training and test datasets you \
should select element numbers in lists. For instance, to select 75% of the \
isolates from ",
 StyleBox["dataSources", "CodeText"],
 " at random to define the training dataset, we proceed as follows:"
}], "Text",
