Cell["\<\
The accuracy of the chosen method in this case is close to other methods and \
it is likely that the best method depends on the specific random selection of \
isolates for the training dataset.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7799551573117375`*^9, 3.7799551913772187`*^9}, {
  3.7799552407709117`*^9, 
  3.7799552619047513`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"015dfff3-bc06-452f-b69c-\
5f6c31d7778d"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

