Cell["\<\
The true positive rate gives the proportion of isolates in the training \
dataset that are correctly attributed to their source. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7799736400561547`*^9, 
  3.779973703349186*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a34b7fd2-3b85-4493-b572-\
9cc21954ddd9"],

